I'd have to take everything down.

09:45.920 --> 09:47.680
I've got my chaos organised.

09:48.680 --> 09:53.280
Where did I put my passport?
Or my ID? Or my wallet?

09:54.560 --> 09:55.880
I lost it again.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.520
