14:01.720 --> 14:03.040
"We are smiling!"

14:29.760 --> 14:33.320
Is Benjamin a little bit cute?
Are you cute, sweetie?

14:34.000 --> 14:38.080
Bianca, sweetie, are you there
with your little brother?

14:52.400 --> 14:55.160
My mum worked in the theatre
four nights a week.

14:55.240 --> 14:58.920
Usually you might have a babysitter
but I made her take me with her.

14:59.680 --> 15:03.280
The smell of those
dark red corridors of GÃ¶ta Lejon.

