I was on this stage with my mum.

22:19.680 --> 22:24.240
And I ran along the whole catwalk,
like, "Come on, Skansen!"

22:24.320 --> 22:25.920
It was full.

22:26.000 --> 22:28.920
Then, about seven or eight years later,

22:29.000 --> 22:33.120
I was on this stage,
yelled, "Come on, Skansen!"

22:33.200 --> 22:35.440
There weren't as many fans.

22:35.520 --> 22:39.640
