tonight, I can yell.

22:39.720 --> 22:41.440
Come on, Skansen!

22:43.600 --> 22:45.280
I can't hear you in the back!

22:47.600 --> 22:49.600
Skansen, I think we can be louder!

22:51.800 --> 22:54.120
